==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quondam
<hw>Quon"dam</hw> <pr>(kw⟦ocr⟧n"d⟦acr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.,
formerly.]</ety> <def>Having been formerly; former; sometime.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧This is the <xex>quondam</xex> king.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

