==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Quondam
<hw>Quon"dam</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person dismissed or ejected from
a position.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Make them
<xex>quondams</xex>; . . . cast them out of their office.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

